  "title": "Earth Crystal - Stardew Valley Wiki",
  "description": "An Earth Crystal is a type of Mineral. It can be foraged in The Mines (especially floors 1 - 39), or obtained from Geodes and Omni Geodes, dropped from Duggies in the Mines (floors 1 - 29), dropped from Haunted Skulls, or from panning. It can also be found in Fishing Treasure Chests or in a Garbage Can.",
